these science projects.

00:08:25.310 --> 00:08:28.820
So I said to him, why don't you
see if music helps a plant grow?

00:08:28.820 --> 00:08:30.160
So we set up two plants.

00:08:30.160 --> 00:08:33.670
We had plant A, plant B and
one the plants got music.

00:08:33.670 --> 00:08:37.970
I think it was Glenn Gould
playing the Goldberg Variations.

00:08:37.970 --> 00:08:40.320
The other plant got no music.

00:08:40.320 --> 00:08:43.490
And surprise, surprise, the
plant that got music grew more.

00:08:43.490 --> 00:08:47.290
But it's not really surprising
because there's been a huge amount

00:08:47.290 --> 00:08:50.680
