has studied exactly this.

00:08:50.680 --> 00:08:52.200
Plants like music.

00:08:52.200 --> 00:08:54.320
They actually have
musical preferences.

00:08:54.320 --> 00:08:58.020
Sometimes they will lean towards
certain music or they'll lean,

00:08:58.020 --> 00:09:01.230
like heavy metal music, they
will lean away against you know,

00:09:01.230 --> 00:09:03.470
