00:10:07.500 --> 00:10:10.010
Now let's go back to Aristotle,

00:10:10.010 --> 00:10:13.300
you can't get much more
old school than Aristotle.

00:10:13.300 --> 00:10:17.070
Aristotle wrote a book
called "The Politics".

00:10:17.070 --> 00:10:19.750
This is one of the two foundational
books in political science.

00:10:19.750 --> 00:10:21.450
If you study ancient
political science,

00:10:21.450 --> 00:10:26.340
you'll read "Plato's Republic"
and Aristotle's "Politics".

00:10:26.340 --> 00:10:30.320
And in Aristotle's "Politics",
he talks at length about music.

00:10:30.320 --> 00:10:34.400
Now that's surprising
to begin with, isn't it?

00:10:34.400 --> 00:10:39.480
That in a book in politics,
Aristotle will write about music.

00:10:40.710 --> 00:10:42.010
