album on with Tony Bennett

00:54:48.390 --> 00:54:50.360
and Queen Latifah is
doing with [inaudible].

00:54:50.360 --> 00:54:54.490
Everyone is doing this
retro jazz stuff.

00:54:54.490 --> 00:54:56.840
