00:59:46.650 --> 00:59:48.060
It's always someone on the fringes.

00:59:48.060 --> 00:59:51.850
So you get these children
of Jewish immigrants hanging

00:59:51.850 --> 00:59:55.100
out with jazz musicians in
Harlem, I'm not surprised at all

00:59:55.100 --> 00:59:57.290
that they came up with innovation.

00:59:57.290 --> 00:59:59.280
Because they didn't have this--

00:59:59.280 --> 01:00:02.090
That's the sense of
shame I'm talking about.

01:00:02.090 --> 01:00:05.760
They had this more-- a
greater way to experiment.

01:00:05.760 --> 01:00:07.350
So yeah, we wouldn't
have the modern love song

01:00:07.350 --> 01:00:09.740
without the Jewish-American
promoters.

