01:01:19.990 --> 01:01:24.950
in the year 100, 1200, 1400
what music would you have heard?

01:01:24.950 --> 01:01:28.130
And the sources are not good
ones, you can read what Herodotus,

01:01:28.130 --> 01:01:31.170
a Greek said there's a great
book by a guy named Mungo Park.

01:01:31.170 --> 01:01:34.860
He was an African traveler
and he went--

01:01:34.860 --> 01:01:36.160
was exploring the interior Africa,

01:01:36.160 --> 01:01:39.760
this would have been 500 years
ago, 400 to 500 years ago.

01:01:39.760 --> 01:01:42.310
And he was sold into
slavery in Africa.

01:01:42.310 --> 01:01:45.200
And was traveling from community
to community and eventually,

01:01:45.200 --> 01:01:48.750
